The mother puts its offspring to
sleep by curling up around them.
It corners foes with speed.

It makes a nest to
suit its long and
skinny body. The nest is impossible
for other POKMON
to enter.

There is no tell
ing where the tail
begins. Despite its short legs, it
is quick at hunt
ing RATTATA.

It lives in narrow
burrows that fit
its slim body. The deeper the nests
go, the more maze
like they become.

FURRET has a very slim build.
When under attack, it can slickly squirm
through narrow spaces and get away. In spite of its short limbs, this
POKMON is very nimble and fleet.

Acurruca a sus cras para que duerman. Acorrala a los
enemigos con su enorme velocidad.

Il fabrique un nid qui convient  son corps trs fin,
et o lui seul peut entrer.

Sein Nest ist seinem schmalen und dnnen Krper

Construye un nido donde introducir su largo y delgado

Il suo nido  adatto al corpo lungo e magro.

Fouinar est trs mince. Lorsquil est attaqu, il peut
senfuir en se faufilant habilement dans les recoins troits.
Malgr ses pattes courtes, ce Pokmon est trs agile
et rapide.

Wiesenior ist sehr schlank. Wenn es angegriffen wird, kann es
sich durch enge Zwischenrume schlngeln und entkommen.
Trotz seiner kurzen Gliedmaen ist dieses Pokmon sehr
wendig und flink.

Furret es de constitucin muy delgada. En combate le resulta
til porque puede escabullirse con habilidad por cualquier
huequito y escapar. A pesar de que tiene patas cortas, es gil
y veloz.

Furret  di esile costituzione. Quando  attaccato riesce
a scappare intrufolandosi in ogni fessura. Nonostante i suoi arti
